data.description:
This fully-furnished apartment is in a duplex featuring 2 bedrooms, two baths and approximately 1000 SF of open floor plan on a lovely lot! Skylight in the bathroom brings in sun light and the crackle of rain in a storm. Large new windows and sliding glass doors mean tons of natural light throughout. Entry door from the attached carport leads into the laundry rooms area which flows into the kitchen. Remodeled living area provides perfect space for small office, studio, or morning coffee spot if you can't get outside to the fenced-in shaded back yard. Bike or walk to shopping, restaurants, theaters, library and just minutes to Mercato! Wiggins Pass State Park is a quick drive to enjoy the peaceful beach at sunset.

Renter responsible for electric and internet + tv. Landlord/owner pays water and sewer.
Pets are allowed for an extra monthly fee of $50 per pet. Complaints from neighbors about noisy and/or problem animals will be grounds for eviction.
No smoking.
Landscaping will be done by landlord/owner.
More details of lease conditions available upon inspection of property.
